00:30:48.496 --> 00:30:51.570
and then it's broken down
to more specifically, focus

00:30:51.570 --> 00:30:53.016
testing and user testing.

00:30:53.016 --> 00:30:55.908
And you may be wondering
why user testing is used

00:30:55.908 --> 00:31:00.484
and that [INAUDIBLE] two
different things, as Sara said,

00:31:00.484 --> 00:31:02.480
it's good to be more granular.

00:31:02.480 --> 00:31:06.402
What we normally refer
to as usability testing,

00:31:06.402 --> 00:31:10.803
as Sara mentioned, has
only fairly recently

00:31:10.803 --> 00:31:12.656
become the standard name for it.

00:31:12.656 --> 00:31:13.280
PROFESSOR: Yes.

00:31:13.280 --> 00:31:13.780
